WEBVTT

00:01:02.840 --> 00:01:05.616
Of course, I knew it was clear

00:01:05.640 --> 00:01:08.536
that religion would be
a principle battlefield

00:01:08.560 --> 00:01:11.016
in this rapidly changing landscape,

00:01:11.040 --> 00:01:12.736
and it was already clear

00:01:12.760 --> 00:01:15.480
that religion was a significant
part of the problem.

00:01:16.120 --> 00:01:17.376
The question for me was,

00:01:17.400 --> 00:01:19.880
could religion
also be part of the solution?

00:01:20.480 --> 00:01:22.096
Now, throughout history,

00:01:22.120 --> 00:01:25.336
people have committed
horrible crimes and atrocities

00:01:25.360 --> 00:01:27.000
in the name of religion.

00:01:28.160 --> 00:01:30.616
And as we entered the 21st century,